name: FixedOrderComparator_compareTest
description: Unit tests for the compare method of FixedOrderComparator.

test_cases.name: testCompareKnownObjects
test_cases.description: Tests the comparison of known objects in FixedOrderComparator.

test_cases.name: testCompareUnknownObjectBehaviorException
test_cases.description: Tests the behavior of FixedOrderComparator when comparing unknown objects, expecting an exception.

test_cases.name: testCompareUnknownObjectBehaviorBefore
test_cases.description: Tests the behavior of FixedOrderComparator when comparing unknown objects set to be placed before known objects.

test_cases.name: testCompareUnknownObjectBehaviorAfter
test_cases.description: Tests the behavior of FixedOrderComparator when comparing unknown objects set to be placed after known objects.

test_cases.name: testAddAndCompare
test_cases.description: Tests adding an unknown object to FixedOrderComparator and then comparing it.

test_cases.name: testAddAsEqualAndCompare
test_cases.description: Tests adding an unknown object as equal to a known object in FixedOrderComparator and then comparing it.

test_cases.name: testIsLocked
test_cases.description: Tests the locking behavior of FixedOrderComparator after a comparison.

test_cases.name: testSetUnknownObjectBehaviorLocked
test_cases.description: Tests setting the unknown object behavior of a locked FixedOrderComparator, expecting an exception.
